Chris Hardman died on March 23 after a long battle with depression . 
  A friend found his body hanged at his home in Lowestoft and identified him at an inquest today . 
  Coroner Peter Dean told the pop star was found hanged at the home by a friend . 
  Mr Hardman shot to fame after appearing on School of Rock . 
  His family said he was 'a huge personality who will be missed'